rules: Rule1: Provided that platform is operational, supply calibrates tool.
Rule2: Whenever technician is assigned to platform, it follows that if it is not the case that functional facility implies accessible region, then vehicle is available.
Rule3: Under the condition that technician is assigned to facility, then if it is not the case that functional facility implies accessible region, vehicle is available.
Rule4: If technician is deployed to region, then either technician is assigned to platform or technician is assigned to facility.

Rule5: Whenever command validates plan, then if command approves operation, and if it is not the case that controls command platform implies successful operation, it is not the case that command is authorized for mission.
Rule6: If command executes order, then command validates plan.
Rule7: Provided that mission completes objective, command executes order.
Rule8: Whenever mission has ongoing objective, command executes order.
Rule9: Under the condition that command monitors mission, then either mission completes objective or mission has ongoing objective.
Rule10: Either command monitors mission or command supervises mission.
Rule11: Whenever vehicle is damaged, vehicle is repaired.
Rule12: Either vehicle is damaged or if command supervises mission, then either mission completes objective or mission has ongoing objective.
Rule13: Provided that supply is loaded onto vehicle, supply transports region.
Rule14: If supply is unloaded from vehicle, then supply transports region.
Rule15: Under the condition that supply is stored at facility, supply is loaded onto vehicle.
Rule16: Either supply is stored at facility or supply is distributed at facility.
Rule17: Either tool is inspected or if supply is distributed at facility, then supply is unloaded from vehicle.
Rule18: Provided that tool is functional, tool is calibrated.
Rule19: If tool is defective, then it is not the case that tool is calibrated.
Rule20: Under the condition that supply is arranged in storage, supply is positioned at facility.
Rule21: If crew is assigned to vehicle, then if it is not the case that moved supply vehicle implies delivers supply facility, supply is arranged in storage.
Rule22: Either crew is assigned to vehicle or crew is assigned to facility.
Rule23: Provided that crew is assigned to facility, then if it is not the case that moved supply vehicle implies delivers supply facility, supply is arranged in storage.
Rule24: Whenever command secures vehicle, it is not the case that command operates facility.
Rule25: Under the condition that supply transports region, then if supply maintains platform, operation is successful.
Rule26: Provided that supply calibrates tool, it is not the case that supply repairs vehicle.
Rule27: If it is not the case that controls command platform implies successful operation, then command is authorized for mission.
Rule28: Provided that it is not the case that controls command platform implies successful operation, it is not the case that command coordinates region.
Rule29: Whenever it is not the case that functional facility implies accessible region, it is not the case that vehicle is available.
Rule30: If it is not the case that it is not the case that controls command platform implies successful operation implies command coordinates region, then command operates facility.
Rule31: Whenever it is not the case that it is not the case that controls command platform implies successful operation implies command coordinates region, command secures vehicle.
Rule32: Provided that it is not the case that it is not the case that transports supply region implies delivers supply facility, platform is operational.
Rule33: If it is not the case that it is not the case that transports supply region implies delivers supply facility, tool is functional.
Rule34: Whenever it is not the case that it is not the case that transports supply region implies delivers supply facility, supply repairs vehicle.
Rule35: If it is not the case that supply transports region, supply is moved by vehicle.
Rule36: Under the condition that it is not the case that supply transports region, it is not the case that supply delivers facility.
Rule37: If it is not the case that operation is successful, facility is functional.
facts: Fact2: Technician is deployed to region.
Fact6: It is not the case that region is accessible.
Fact7: It is not the case that vehicle is repaired.
Fact8: It is not the case that tool is inspected.
Fact9: It is not the case that supply is positioned at facility.
